Added a generic `Image` component that centralises the absolute-vs-relative download URL decision for e-Processos image fields, and registered it in the Volto components registry. Updated `resolveEprocessosAssetUrl` to treat absolute upstream URLs (sapl_documentos / sapl_documentos_download patterns) as direct e-Processos assets and return them verbatim, bypassing Volto's substring-based `isInternalURL`. Consumer components (Participantes, Sumario) honour absolute URLs emitted by the backend when `eprocessos.proxy_images` is false. @ericof
